title: Modern Apt. for rent in desirable West Medford
posting_body: ['NO FEE - 3BR Modern Apt.', 'on 1st floor available for rent in West Medford (Prestigious and desirable location).', 'It is the *', 'Most* convenient location for public transportation and easy access to routes 2, 93, 60, 16 and Tufts University.', 'Literally 5 minute walk to the traveler (commuter) rail (12 min.', 'ride to Boston, north station), Close to bus line as well red line & orange line.', 'House is de-leaded.', 'Amenities:', '- Separate Dining and Living', '- Onsite Car Parking', '- Large Deck', '- Back Yard - BBQ area', '- Laundry', 'In the Basement', '- Full Size Bathroom', '- All modern amenities (Dishwasher, Disposal, Gas Stove...)', '- Energy star windows.', '- Natural Gas heat (save bill this winter!!!)', '- Plenty of closet space and additional storage in basement', '- Walk to West Medford Center (Shops, Dunkin Donuts, Restaurants,', 'Brooks pharmacy, public and private school)', 'Apt. is available 8/15 - Text/call 617 899-2753']
